# Next.js Rules

- Use App Router (`app/`) with `page.tsx`, `layout.tsx`, `loading.tsx`, `error.tsx`
- Server Components by default â€” add `'use client'` only when necessary (event handlers, hooks, browser APIs)
- Named exports over default exports: `export function Button() {}`
- kebab-case for directories: `components/auth-form/`
- PascalCase for component files: `AuthForm.tsx`
- Use `next/image` for all images, `next/link` for navigation
- Fetch data in Server Components, pass down as props
- Route handlers go in `app/api/**/route.ts`
- Use `generateMetadata()` for dynamic SEO metadata
- Prefer `loading.tsx` + Suspense over manual loading states
- Use `notFound()`, `redirect()` from `next/navigation` in server context
